{"tid":2398831,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨新年致辭：屌你老母臭拜登 肯傾未呀? 合作共贏呀","createTime":"2021-02-07T15:31:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T18:41:45.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7694510bc85c3780fb03521ab36e5bf8baca5987","tid":2398831,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:31:04.000Z","msg":"王毅指中美關係面臨節點 願秉持合作共贏精神重啟對話<br />\n<br />\n國務委員兼外長王毅向駐華使團發表新年致辭，指中美關係作為世界最重要的雙邊關係，面臨關鍵節點，中方願意秉持不衝突不對抗、相互尊重、合作共贏精神，重啟對話協商，積極管控分歧，聚焦互利合作，推動兩國關係回到健康穩定發展的軌道。<br />\n<br />\n王毅說，中國在新一年會與各國守望相助，爭取早日獲得抗疫勝利，並與各國並肩合作，促進全球經濟恢復發展，加強往來，維護國際局勢和平穩定，不斷提升中俄新時代全面戰略協作夥伴關係，持續增進中歐政治互信和務實合作。<br />\n<br />\n王毅又說，中國將更堅定倡導和踐行多邊主義，主動參與建設以聯合國為主導的有效多邊機制，更積極推動建立公平合理的全球治理體系。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574624-20210207.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574624-20210207.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOU6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=e5b73886\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574624-20210207.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7a112bfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574624-20210207.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"d38a00a1c7a491a2cd3357c2651cf4274c5f4567","tid":2398831,"uid":21545,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:55:54.000Z","msg":"I am joe Biden and I forgot this message <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b1dfce4eb2c910513364e4f5fffefa275455bdf","tid":2398831,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d38a00a1c7a491a2cd3357c2651cf4274c5f4567","tid":2398831,"uid":21545,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T15:55:54.000Z","msg":"I am joe Biden and I forgot this message <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2